name: cucky cyberpunk
description: cucky the rabbit character with cyberpunk concept in pepe and meme series. he is a subordinate of choiros who is the boss of a very famous scamer member in the metaverse world. cucky is a swordsman who has a calm but slippery nature. he comes from a poor samurai clan. with his pet cat who is also a street cat. want to rule the world of metaverse and kill members of cyberspace especially pepe and memes.
